{"tid":915221,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"來看看台灣有多蠢吧. 公投自行放棄台灣正名機會, 票差100萬票","createTime":"2018-11-24T20:43:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-26T07:09:07.000Z","uid":147756,"like":28,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b5188cf3ac5a54402749a203be01e3fd42d5dc6c","tid":915221,"uid":147756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T20:43:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/25/042548_2d934284a7b477f4277bc41429e11ad2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F25%2F042548_2d934284a7b477f4277bc41429e11ad2.png&h=39ad0556&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\">107年全民性公民投票 - 第13案<br />\n</span></strong></span><a href=\"http://referendum.2018.nat.gov.tw/pc/zh_TW/07/00000000000000000.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Freferendum.2018.nat.gov.tw%2Fpc%2Fzh_TW%2F07%2F00000000000000000.html&d=8zFlkMM53qITZ6U1f%2FK3gMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=a81e5832\" target=\"_blank\">http://referendum.2018.nat.gov.tw/pc/zh_TW/07/00000000000000000.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>應該港友都知道台灣參加不少國際賽事跟奧運, 都只能以中華台北跟體委會會旗參賽吧. <br />\n不能以台灣與台灣國旗參加, 台灣今日公投, 最重要的對中國的這項</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>加上因為這次2020東京奧運是日本舉辦的, 日本似乎有表意要幫台灣改回來<br />\n但剛剛開票結束, 結果... <span style=\"color: green;\">台灣人自己放棄正名台灣的機會.....</span><br />\n<br />\n看來<strong><strong><span style=\"color: navy;\">台灣獨立公投</span></strong></strong>可能也不用期待多少了, <br />\n可能也是支持統一(被統一)會超過50%, 甚至6比4的機會存在吧.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">歡迎港友表達意見<br />\n<br />\n台灣人蠢, 請點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n台灣人聰明, 請點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>"},{"pid":"0e786265bdd88cfdd281f30fa53d72656e80c2b3","tid":915221,"uid":203431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T21:02:32.000Z","msg":"歡迎台灣加入特別行政區的一份子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/smile_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f87565c2e7b155a7987a2ed1599cdf301232f54e","tid":915221,"uid":37081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T23:05:42.000Z","msg":"有唔少深綠唔滿意落係台灣「國」而反對"},{"pid":"56877cccfc29882751373e7560b3bcdf86bc8425","tid":915221,"uid":147756,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f87565c2e7b155a7987a2ed1599cdf301232f54e","tid":915221,"uid":37081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T23:05:42.000Z","msg":"有唔少深綠唔滿意落係台灣「國」而反對"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T23:39:05.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">喜樂島聯盟 Formosa Alliance</span></strong></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.vote2019.com.tw/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vote2019.com.tw%2F&d=8zFlkMM53qITZ6U1f%2FK3gMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=2a8bf87b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.vote2019.com.tw/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>台灣國是<span style=\"color: blue;\">獨立公投</span>課題部份了, <br />\n那部分獨立公投喜樂島聯盟在努力爭取中了<br />\n<br />\n不過看到今天這種投票結果, <br />\n感覺搞不好也是投統一居多的可能性存在, <br />\n那就會變成沒有必要改國號了<br />\n<br />\n只是這本來就比奧運正名難推出來, 所以這次奧運正名沒成功, <br />\n也許有機會連帶連獨立公投都沒辦法成功推出</strong>"},{"pid":"0434bf1dc6daa8792ebea9881741276a2bd4cf18","tid":915221,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T23:45:12.000Z","msg":"焦島"},{"pid":"9f2f2add115bc6947e2b8879f8c0ea5fe87fcfdb","tid":915221,"uid":87073,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T23:53:44.000Z","msg":"怪錯左應采兒<br />\n原來有一半台狗都係縮骨"},{"pid":"699e223ca5e0f967b8e90264b3699ca0033628df","tid":915221,"uid":34308,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T01:55:43.000Z","msg":"明日香港<br />\n同香港啲老野一樣<br />\n諗住唔搞事共產黨就唔搞你"},{"pid":"af61cb5d41301be4464dd99d03fc4ea0949d0571","tid":915221,"uid":55555,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T02:00:21.000Z","msg":"投票前仲以為呢項一定通過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75ddeb66726e4c434ee73307a1181c86991d70fb","tid":915221,"uid":24024,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T02:01:33.000Z","msg":"你都on9<br />\n奧委會講明如果正名咗 有機會唔比運動員出戰奧運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n運動員練咁耐就係為一次奧運機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5103aab6666ad15bde762f1e1c13d33e3d7b3803","tid":915221,"uid":202354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T02:02:46.000Z","msg":"我覺得台灣係兩岸關係上保持曖昧關係就最好,不統不獨,主張九二共識"},{"pid":"30fc7df1db5e908f0e883cb63a9f9ec08aaa967e","tid":915221,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T06:48:26.000Z","msg":"「這次2020東京奧運是日本舉辦的, 日本似乎有表意要幫台灣改回來」<br />\n國際奧委會唔撚俾, 日本舉辦咁又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n醒少少當幫忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"483b2c7d61336e942c27f2d28f07cd83199ee53d","tid":915221,"uid":109923,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T06:50:45.000Z","msg":"原來奥運係日本話曬事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n天真"},{"pid":"8b85fd1e8b60d3b95c62a020ffb4d2e73483e3b3","tid":915221,"uid":107405,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T07:09:07.000Z","msg":"鬼叫支共霸道咩 <br />\n你估d台灣人個心唔想正名 只係個個都心知咁做一定會比人打壓 所以寧願保持現狀 呢點亦係老美願意支持台灣既條件<br />\n<br />\n就好似之前聯合國單野咁 拎住台灣護照連去人權理事會旁聽都比人趕出黎<br />\n呢個公投就算成功 運動員係正名後係注定100%無得出場 因為支共會不顧一切打壓佢地 即使要駛錢駛橫手<br />\n<br />\n都係個句 支共一日不滅 香港同台灣都無好日子過"}]}